ObjectiveTextPools[8]="Commander: while we repelled the initial ADVENT invasion force, we were unable to keep them from eliminating the Resistance leadership in the area. Without leaders we will not be able to maintain control of this region and will need to pull back until we can locate new contacts in this area willing to lead the movement."

