[StasisVestProject X2TechTemplate]
DisplayName="Stasis Vests"
Summary="In addition to granting a health bonus, the Stasis vest is designed to restore hit points to wounded soldiers during battle."

[HellweaveProject X2TechTemplate]
DisplayName="Hellweave"
Summary="The Hellweave is designed to both protect the wearer and inflict damage on enemy melee attackers and set them aflame."

[AlloyPlatingProject X2TechTemplate]
DisplayName="Alloy Plating"
Summary="This improvement on our ceramic plating should offer additional ablative protection for our soldiers."

[ChameleonSuitProject X2TechTemplate]
DisplayName="Chameleon Suit"
Summary="While this design will not afford any bonus protection, it allows our troops to blend in whatever environment they are operating in, reducing the time necessary to infiltrate enemy targets."

[CarapacePlatingProject X2TechTemplate]
DisplayName="Carapace Plating"
Summary="This upgraded plating set draws from some old XCOM designs to provide significant ablative protection for the troops."

